    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40-2018 framework. Experimental validation demonstrates RH prediction error within the ±0.15 acceptance band across all five operating points. GCI of 1.8% confirms adequate mesh resolution. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
